Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/LiquidFire/dotvim.git

Create symlinks (Unix):

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Create symlinks (Windows):

    mklink /D vimfiles .vim
    mklink _vimrc _vimfiles/vimrc

Fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Update a bundle:

    cd ~/.vim/bundle/foo
    git pull
